# Cat Scratch Fever
A roadmap-style card game built in Godot.

## Status
🚧 Early Development - Currently building database systems and UI

## Quick Start
1. Open in Godot 4.x
2. Run the project

## Project Structure
- `/scenes/ui` - UI scenes
- `/scripts/databases` - Database scripts (song_database.gd)
- `/assets` - Art, audio, fonts

## Current Work
- Building song database system
- Designing card mechanics
- Implementing card database
- Working towards MVP
